Subject: [PATCH] Convert coaching form into a modal

- 1-to-1 and Group coaching cards are now clickable triggers
- Clicking a card opens a modal with the request form, pre-selecting the chosen coaching type
- Modal closes via close button, overlay click, or Escape; body scroll locked while open

